snippet.title: Isotower 2018 Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Isotower is an upcoming Skyscraper Management Tycoon game, developed by Todd Barchok.

Find out more about Isotower at http://isotower.com/

Trailer Music is Boulevard St Germain by Jahzzar. The full song can be downloaded at http://freemusicarchive.org/music/Jahzzar/Paris_Lisboa/Boulevard_St_Germain
